    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Followed at MUHC Heart Function Centre

          -  Documented EF of less than or equal to 35% and an enlarged heart with a left
             ventricular end-diastolic size of greater than 6 cm.

          -  Patient's written consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with a known underlying condition that results in a weakened and enlarged
             heart

          -  Patients unable to read and understand the consent form

          -  Patients who do not wish to participate
      </textblock>
